&lt;b&gt;- Where are we today?&lt;/b&gt;
Nobody knows where to start when looking for documentation. There are too many choices!

&lt;b&gt;- Why is this a problem?&lt;/b&gt;
Finding documentation is too hard, even when good docs exists.

&lt;b&gt;- The proposed enhancement:&lt;/b&gt;
We need a single main official blessed directory for finding documentation.

&lt;b&gt;- Exit criteria:&lt;/b&gt;
existence of said directory.

Comments:
The directory should be external, possibly with an internal version. We also need to figure out where the main docs repository is going to be; maybe chromium.org sites?
